      <guid>http://localhost:1313/lippold/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;We are partnering with &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.instagram.com/fargoskateboarding/&#34;&gt;Fargo Skateboarding&lt;/a&gt; &amp;amp; Crystal Lake Park District to redesign the Lippold Skatepark in Crystal Lake. Fargo put together the design &amp;amp; proposal that was submitted to the Park District in April 2026. Currently, the park district is getting bids from contractors. We should hear more this summer!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;iframe src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/files/lippold_conceptual_design.pdf&#34; width=&#34;100%&#34; height=&#34;800px&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;</description>
