      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;saturday-april-18&#34;&gt;Saturday, April 18&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;📍 Ryan Buss Zone Skatepark&lt;/strong&gt; — McHenry, IL&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re at home base this Saturday. 8am til 11 ish - Probably later!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;All ages and skill levels welcome — come skate with us.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free coffee provided by the homies at &lt;a href=&#34;https://headycup.com/&#34;&gt;Heady Cup Coffee Roasters&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/strong&gt; They roast &amp;amp; brew right here in McHenry. Check em out!&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;</description>
